# Download the bash and python scripts at the same time.
# Modify the configuration information about omruntime and openLooKeng1.2.
    #omniruntime config
    server=localhost:8090
    binpath=/root/code/lab/hetu-core/hetu-server/target/hetu-server-1.2.0-SNAPSHOT/bin
    clientpath=$binpath/hetu-cli-1.2.0-SNAPSHOT-executable.jar

    #olk1.2 config
    server=localhost:8080
    binpath=/opt/olk/hetu-server-1.2.0/bin
    clientpath=$binpath/hetu-cli-1.2.0-executable.jar

# Directly run the bash omni-operator-perf.sh script.
The running result is saved in the folder starting with /opt/omniruntime/result_. Each SQL statement is saved in a folder.
The script runs omniruntime and olk1.2 at the same time. Each SQL statement is executed six times, and the JSON file is captured and saved in the JSON folder. Then, the average value is calculated for the second to fifth times, and the results are saved in the avg_result file for comparison. Generate a bar line chart and save it in the charter folder.

#将bash脚本和python脚本同时下载下来
#修改对应集成了omruntime的openLooKeng和openLooKeng1.2相关的配置信息
#直接运行脚本bash omni-operator-perf.sh
运行结果保存在/opt/omniruntime/result_开头的文件夹中，每个sql一个文件夹，保存
脚本会同时运行omniruntime和olk1.2,每条sql执行6次并抓取json文件保存在json文件夹中，然后针对第2-5次求平均值，结果保存在avg_result文件里，并用其进行对比，生成柱状折线图，保存在charter文件夹
